102
00:04:50,169 --> 00:04:53,172
HOMER: D'oh!
Can't... breathe.

103
00:04:53,256 --> 00:04:55,508
-Too many... children.
-(thudding continues)

104
00:04:57,927 --> 00:05:01,514
(scattered boos)

105
00:05:01,597 --> 00:05:03,391
Eyewitnesses estimate
the man's weight

106
00:05:03,474 --> 00:05:06,019
<i>at somewhere between</i>
<i>400 and 500 pounds.</i>

107
00:05:06,102 --> 00:05:08,021
<i>And now on the lighter side</i>
<i>of the news,</i>

108
00:05:08,104 --> 00:05:10,773
<i>-and I use the term loosely. (chuckles) </i>
-D'oh!

109
00:05:10,857 --> 00:05:14,193
<i>-(reporters shouting)</i>
<i>-No, the slide is perfectly safe.</i>

110
00:05:14,277 --> 00:05:16,696
<i>-This was an isolated incident.</i>
<i>-I understand that, Krusty.</i>

111
00:05:16,779 --> 00:05:18,781
<i>But, Krusty, isn't that</i>
<i>exactly what you said</i>

112
00:05:18,865 --> 00:05:21,200
